   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="abstract" resp="kg">
            <p>
               <rs type="event" ref="ev__QGW_II_II_3675"><rs type="fn" role="issuer"><rs
                        type="person" ref="pe__anna_SB_CD_00249">Anna, <rs type="person"
                           ref="pe__leopold_holczler_QGW_II_II_3675"><roleName type="title"
                              >hern</roleName> Leupolts des Hölczler</rs>
                        <roleName type="kin" corresp="pe__leopold_holczler_QGW_II_II_3675"
                           >hausfrau</roleName>, die emaln Hainreichen den Haiden auch <roleName
                           type="kin" corresp="pe__heinrich_haiden_QGW_II_II_2564"
                           >eleichen</roleName> gehabt hat</rs>,</rs>
                  <triggerstring n="disp">stiftet</triggerstring>
                  <triggerstring n="reason">für ihr, ihrer <rs type="person"
                        ref="pe__helena_QGW_II_II_3675"><roleName type="kin"
                           corresp="pe__anna_SB_CD_00249">Mutter</roleName>
                        <roleName type="title">fraun</roleName> Helen der Sibenlinderin</rs>, ihres
                     ersten Mannes, ihrer Vorfahren und Nachkommen Seelenheil</triggerstring>
                  <triggerstring n="disp">eine Messe</triggerstring>, <triggerstring n="impl_rules">virstund
                     in der wochen</triggerstring>
                  <rs type="fn" role="recipient">auf <rs type="org"
                        ref="org__wien-st_stephan-altar_st_maria">Unserr Fraun altar in
                        Allerheiligen tumbkirchen dacz sand Steffan</rs></rs>
                  <triggerstring n="impl_rules">zu lesen</triggerstring>, <triggerstring n="disp"
                        ><add>verleiht</add></triggerstring>
                  <rs type="fn" role="other"><triggerstring n="fn">verleiht dieselbe
                        zuerst</triggerstring>
                     <rs type="person" ref="pe__martin_wienner_QGW_II_II_3675"><roleName
                           type="title">hern</roleName> Mertten Wienner von Swabdorf <roleName
                           type="occ"
                           corresp="org__wien-st_stephan-altar_st_maria-messe_auf_der_saeule_johann"
                              ><add>Kaplan</add></roleName></rs></rs>
                  <triggerstring n="disp">und widmet dazu</triggerstring>: a) <rs type="fn" role="other"
                        ><triggerstring n="fn">mit Handen</triggerstring>
                     <rs type="person" ref="pe__johann_hemel_QGW_II_II_3675">Hannsen Hêmel, der <rs
                           type="person" ref="pe__margarethe_QGW_II_II_3675"><roleName type="title"
                              >edeln</roleName>
                           <roleName type="title">fraun</roleName> Margreten der Liechtenhoferin zum
                           Liechtenstain</rs>
                        <roleName type="occ" corresp="pe__margarethe_QGW_II_II_3675"
                           select="pl__maria_enzersdorf">ambtman</roleName> zu Entschestorf</rs>,
                        <rs type="person" ref="pe__niklas_lukchner_QGW_II_II_3675">Niclasen des
                        Lukchner, <rs type="person" ref="pe__johann_hindernpach_QGW_II_II_3675"
                              ><roleName type="title">maister</roleName> Hannsen Hindernpach,
                              <roleName type="prof">lerer bäbstlicher rechten</roleName>, <roleName
                              type="occ" corresp="org__moedling">pharrer</roleName> zu Medling</rs>,
                           <roleName type="occ" corresp="pe__johann_hindernpach_QGW_II_II_3675"
                           >ambtman</roleName></rs>, und <rs type="person"
                        ref="pe__johann_kuffner_QGW_II_II_3675">Hannsen des Küfner, des <rs
                           type="person" ref="pe__wolfgang_von_wallsee_QGW_II_II_3675"><roleName
                              type="title">edeln</roleName>
                           <roleName type="title">herren</roleName>, <roleName type="title"
                              >hern</roleName> Wolfgangs von Walsse, <roleName type="occ"
                              corresp="org__oesterreich-herzogtum">obristen marschalh</roleName> in
                           Österreich, <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__steyr">obristen
                              drugksessen</roleName> in Steir und <unclear instant="false"><roleName
                                 type="occ" corresp="org__oesterreich-herzogtum">haubtmans ob der
                                 Enns</roleName></unclear></rs>, <roleName type="occ"
                           corresp="pe__wolfgang_von_wallsee_QGW_II_II_3675">ambtman</roleName> zu
                        Medling</rs>,</rs>
                  <rs type="fn" role="transactiongood_I"><rs type="place" ref="pl__moedling-immo_18"
                           ><roleName type="owner" corresp="pe__anna_SB_CD_00249">einen</roleName>
                        Weingarten, <roleName type="topo" corresp="pl__moedling">gelegen daselbs zu
                           Medling im Hochprunn</roleName>, genant der Phanczagel, zenagst <rs
                           type="place" ref="pl__moedling-immo_19"><roleName type="owner"
                              corresp="org__wien-schotten">der Schotten</roleName> weingarten</rs>
                        <roleName type="topo" corresp="pl__moedling-immo_19"><add>zenagst</add> an
                           aim rain</roleName>, <rs type="event" ref="ev__QGW_II_II_3675_men_1"><rs
                              type="fn" role="issuer">von <rs type="place"
                                 ref="pl__moedling-immo_18">dem</rs> man</rs>
                           <rs type="fn" role="recipient"><rs type="person"
                                 ref="pe__margarethe_QGW_II_II_3675">der Lichtenhoferin in ir vesten
                                 Liechtenstain</rs>,</rs>
                           <add>je</add>
                           <rs type="fn" role="transactiongood_I"><measure><add>5
                                 Helbling</add></measure>
                              <add>zu</add>
                              <triggerstring n="fn"><add>Grunddienst</add></triggerstring>
                              <triggerstring n="disp"><add>Grunddienst</add>
                                 <add>dient</add></triggerstring></rs></rs>
                        <rs type="event" ref="ev__QGW_II_II_3675"><rs type="fn" role="issuer"
                                 ><add>von</add>
                              <rs type="place" ref="pl__moedling-immo_18"><add>dem</add></rs>
                              <add>man</add></rs>
                           <rs type="fn" role="recipient">dem <rs type="org"
                                 ref="org__moedling-pfarre">Pfarrer zu Mödling</rs></rs>
                           <add>je</add>
                           <rs type="fn" role="transactiongood_I"><measure><add>5
                                 Helbling</add></measure>
                              <add>zu</add>
                              <triggerstring n="fn"><add>Grunddienst</add></triggerstring>
                              <triggerstring n="disp"><add>Grunddienst</add>
                                 <add>dient</add></triggerstring></rs></rs>
                        <rs type="event" ref="ev__QGW_II_II_3675_men_3">und <rs type="fn"
                              role="issuer"><add>von</add>
                              <rs type="place" ref="pl__moedling-immo_18"><add>dem</add></rs>
                              <add>man</add></rs>
                           <rs type="fn" role="recipient">dem <rs type="person"
                                 ref="pe__wolfgang_von_wallsee_QGW_II_II_3675">Herrn von
                                 Wallsee</rs></rs> je <rs type="fn" role="transactiongood_I"
                                 ><measure>5 Helbling</measure> zu <triggerstring n="fn"
                                 >Grunddienst</triggerstring>
                              <triggerstring n="disp"><add>Grunddienst</add>
                           dient</triggerstring></rs></rs></rs></rs> b) <rs type="fn" role="other"
                        ><triggerstring n="fn">mit Handen</triggerstring>
                     <rs type="person" ref="pe__anna_QGW_II_II_3626"><roleName type="title"
                           >swester</roleName> Annen Vösendorfferin, <roleName type="occ"
                           corresp="org__wien-st_niklas_vor_dem_stubentor_zisterzienserinnen"
                           >abtessin</roleName> des fraunklosters zu sand Niclas vor Stubentor zu
                        Wienn</rs>,</rs>
                  <rs type="fn" role="transactiongood_I"><rs type="place"
                        ref="pl__wien-immo_jeus_vor_stubentor_3"><roleName type="owner"
                           corresp="pe__anna_SB_CD_00249">ihren</roleName> Weingarten, <roleName
                           type="topo" corresp="pl__wien-jeus_vor_stubentor">gelegen daselbs vor
                           Stubentor auf dem Yeus</roleName>, das ain viertail ist, <roleName
                           type="topo" corresp="pl__wien-immo_jeus_vor_stubentor_2"
                           >zenagst</roleName>
                        <rs type="place" ref="pl__wien-immo_jeus_vor_stubentor_2" cert="medium"
                              ><roleName type="owner" corresp="org__wien-dominikaner">der
                              Prediger</roleName> weingarten</rs>, <rs type="event"
                           ref="ev__QGW_II_II_3675_men_1"><rs type="fn" role="issuer">von <rs
                                 type="place" ref="pl__wien-immo_jeus_vor_stubentor_3">dem</rs>
                              man</rs>
                           <rs type="fn" role="recipient"><rs type="org"
                                 ref="org__wien-st_niklas_vor_dem_stubentor_zisterzienserinnen"
                              /></rs>
                           <rs type="fn" role="transactiongood_I"><measure>85 dn.</measure> zu
                                 <triggerstring n="fn">Grunddienst</triggerstring></rs>
                           <triggerstring n="disp"><add>Grunddienst</add>
                     dient</triggerstring></rs></rs>.</rs>
                  <triggerstring n="impl_rules">Die Lehenschaft der Messe soll nach ihrem Tode ihrem
                     Manne, nach dessen Ableben ihrem Sohne Larencz dem Haiden und dem jeweilig
                     ältesten Descendenten desselben, nach deren Aussterben dem Bürgermeister und
                     Rathe zustehen.</triggerstring></rs>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div type="seal">
            <p><rs type="event" ref="ev__QGW_II_II_3675"><rs type="fn" role="witness">Siegler: <rs
                        type="person" ref="pe__leopold_holczler_QGW_II_II_3675">Leupolt der
                        Hölczler</rs>, <rs type="person" ref="pe__margarethe_QGW_II_II_3675"
                           ><roleName type="title">frau</roleName> Margret die Liechtenhoferin mit
                        ihrem gruntinsigil, das zu der vesten Liechtenstain gehoret</rs>, <rs
                        type="person" ref="pe__niklas_lukchner_QGW_II_II_3675">Niclas der
                        Lukchner</rs>, <rs type="person" ref="pe__johann_kuffner_QGW_II_II_3675"
                        >Hanns Kuffner</rs>, <rs type="person" ref="pe__anna_QGW_II_II_3626">die
                           <roleName type="occ"
                           corresp="org__wien-st_niklas_vor_dem_stubentor_zisterzienserinnen"
                           >Aebtissin</roleName> von sand Niklas</rs> und der <rs type="person"
                        ref="pe__ulrich_hirssauer_QGW_II_II_3239">Wiener <roleName type="occ"
                           corresp="org__wien">Stadtschreiber</roleName> Ulreich
                     Hirssauer</rs>.</rs></rs>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div type="nota">
            <p>Indorsate: a) ain stiftbrieff über Unsser Fraun altar in Allerheiligen tuemkirchen
               dacz sandt Steffan. b) Ich hab nie nichts erfragen künden. </p>
         </div>
